One can login through the "MyDolomiti" community, after having registered (free of charge) to use the services. The APP offers useful information such as the open/closed status of individual lifts and slopes in real time, opening hours of the lifts, breaks, weather forecasts, points of interest such as ski schools, ski rentals, infopoints, Pick-up Box, as well as descriptions and contacts. 
The user will also find other interesting and popular functions, such as the Performance Check, Tracking option to record the route taken while skiing, Routing which will navigate you to a predetermined point on the slopes. By reaching certain goals with the "Tracking" function, the user will be assigned interesting Badges - a great way to challenge yourself! And finally, you get to play too since the registered members of the APP-community can also have fun with the APP's game functions, creating their network of friends, who must also be registered members and in possession of a Dolomiti Superski ski pass and challenging each other throughout the ski season.
Discover the new APP’s full potential watching the video tutorials.

- For SPORT PLAYERS:
 
Tenniscall is a sport booking app with lots of social networking features. On the one hand, you can easily book a court online (tennis, padel, soccer, etc.) provided that your sports center has joined our platform; on the other hand, you can chat with other players in your area and invite friends or new people to play a game (with or without score). Tenniscall allows you to organize challenges, share results and track your performance. On Tenniscall you will also be able to create and manage groups and friendly competitions, such as tournaments and leagues.
 
- For TENNIS CLUBS and SPORTS CENTERS:
 
Tenniscall is a free sports venue management software helping businesses to manage their activities online: court bookings, private / group classes, calendar management, reporting, customers registry, medical certificates, club memberships, tournaments, etc. The Tenniscall management system is accessible anywhere and at any time via phone, computer and tablet and stands out for being complete, easy to use and intuitive. The use of Tenniscall does not require any type of training or technical expertise. If you are the owner of a club or sports center, immediately request access to your management account to see how it works: https://www.tenniscall.com/en/tennis-court-booking-system
